text: Papeete is the capital city of French Polynesia, an overseas collectivity of the French Republic. The commune is located on the north-west of the island of Tahiti in the Pacific Ocean. As of 2017, there were 26,926 people living there. ==References== Category:1818 establishments Category:Capital cities in Oceania Category:Communes in France Category:French Polynesia
title: Papeete
